00:17:20,838 --> 00:17:22,556
Whoo hoo hoo hoo!
Here we go!

526
00:17:22,557 --> 00:17:25,358
Get him!
Aim for the joints!

527
00:17:25,359 --> 00:17:26,359
Cool cool cool!
Cool cool cool!

528
00:17:26,360 --> 00:17:27,527
- Take that!
- Get him!

529
00:17:27,528 --> 00:17:29,396
Die, racism!

530
00:17:29,397 --> 00:17:30,664
[Groans]

531
00:17:30,665 --> 00:17:32,098
