534
00:17:35,903 --> 00:17:39,739
[Groaning]

535
00:17:39,740 --> 00:17:41,241
Take that!
[Laughs]

536
00:17:41,242 --> 00:17:44,277
- Aah!
- Aah! Oh, no! Aah!

537
00:17:44,278 --> 00:17:45,796
[Laughs]

538
00:17:45,797 --> 00:17:50,634
Hey!
